INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:
+------------------------+

If you're running rsync as a daemon, kill it:

# killall rsync

Then, upgrade the package:

# upgradepkg rsync-2.5.7-i486-1.tgz

Finally, restart the rsync daemon:

# rsync --daemon


